metadata.name: DC Franchise Rankings Database
metadata.description: Complete player rankings for all 68 players across all seasons

rankings.title: The Strategist
rankings.reasoning: THREE finals appearances (unprecedented). WINNER of Season 4 (7-6-1 closest finale ever). Most challenge wins in franchise (13 total). Fire-making champion (beat Gwen at F4). Strategic mastermind across all three seasons. Runner-up twice before finally winning his crown.

rankings.title: The Quiet Threat
rankings.reasoning: PERFECT GAME (zero votes all season). Elite challenge performance (5 immunity wins). Dominated from start to finish in Season 5. Unbreakable bond with Jay. Unanimous jury vote (8-0-0). Proved that being underestimated is the ultimate strategy.

rankings.title: The Perfectionist
rankings.reasoning: PERFECT GAME Season 3 winner (4-3-1). Zero votes all season. Strategic rank #1. Only 2 votes against across 2 seasons. Near-flawless gameplay with minimal errors. Elite strategic and social control.

rankings.title: The Competitor
rankings.reasoning: Most challenge wins by a female (9 total). THREE seasons of consistent performance. F4 across all appearances. Back-to-back-back-back immunities (S4 Ep 11-14 consecutive). Clutch fire-making loser but elite competitor. Never won but always a threat.

rankings.title: The Social Queen
rankings.reasoning: Season 1 winner (5-4). ONLY 1 vote against all season (cleanest winner S1). TWO finals appearances. Perfect social bonds. Lost S2 finale but still elite social player. Proof that loyalty and likeability can win.

rankings.title: The Survivor
rankings.reasoning: TWO finals appearances (never won). Most challenge wins across 2 seasons (8 total). Longest idol hold (9 tribals S4). Perfect idol plays. Elite physical + strategic player. Always a bridesmaid, never a bride.

rankings.title: The Underdog
rankings.reasoning: Season 2 winner (5-3-1). Survived CONSTANT targeting. Earned jury respect despite adversity. Clutch immunity wins when needed. Proof that survival > control. Won despite being the biggest target.

rankings.title: The Loyalist
rankings.reasoning: UNPRECEDENTED 3 unbreakable bonds simultaneously (S4). Only 1 vote against all season (cancelled). Perfect idol plays. Lost closest finale ever (6 jury votes). Elite social bonds. Loyalty specialist.

rankings.title: The Underestimated
rankings.reasoning: TWO finals appearances. Strategic rank #1 (S3). Controlled merge phase S3. Unbreakable bond specialist. Consistent F3 finishes. Brain over brawn strategy.

rankings.title: The Villain
rankings.reasoning: THREE seasons (elite longevity). Strategic gameplay across all appearances. Villain archetype. Merge maker in all seasons. 27 votes against (target status). Never won but always memorable.

rankings.title: The Analyst
rankings.reasoning: Strategic partner to Alejandro (S4). Unbreakable bond. Elite strategic mind. Made jury. Strong social reads. Underrated strategic player.

rankings.title: The Challenge Beast
rankings.reasoning: 5 challenge wins Season 1 (4 immunity + 1 reward). F3 finish. Physical threat. Tiebreaker juror. Strong early-merge player. Athletic prowess.

rankings.title: The Fighter
rankings.reasoning: TWO seasons. Most votes against across career (32 total). Survived adversity. Made jury both times. Fighter mentality. High threat but resilient.

rankings.title: The Multi-Faceted
rankings.reasoning: TWO seasons. Strong social player. Made merge both times. Challenge competitor. Likeable personality. Solid mid-tier player.

rankings.title: The Powerhouse
rankings.reasoning: Physical threat. Strong competitor in Season 5. Challenge performance. Leadership qualities. Made jury.

rankings.title: The Survivalist
rankings.reasoning: Season 5 finalist (2nd place). Strong strategic game. Challenge competitor. Made it to the end. Solid gameplay.

rankings.title: The Loyal Friend
rankings.reasoning: Most loyal player S2. Made jury. 22 votes against (2nd most S1). Loyalty over strategy. Cast only Lindsay jury vote. Heart over head.

rankings.title: The Follower
rankings.reasoning: TWO seasons. Alejandro's target (S2 meltdown). Made jury S1. Unbreakable bond partner. Mid-merge player. Musician archetype.

rankings.title: The Chaos Agent
